    <item><title>ChristianMahnke.de: Painting by Kaczmarek Tadeusz (1937-2006)</title>
        <link>https://christianmahnke.de/post/painting-kaczmarek-tadeusz</link>
        <pubDate>Thu, 23 Jan 2025 17:18:44 +0200</pubDate>
        <guid>https://projektemacher.org/en/post/christianmahnke/post/painting-kaczmarek-tadeusz/</guid>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;I have found a painting by &lt;a href=&#34;https://jbc.jelenia-gora.pl/dlibra/publication/45520/edition/41040/content&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Kaczmarek Tadeusz&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;https://jbc-jelenia--gora-pl.translate.goog//Content/41040/kaczmarek.html?_x_tr_sl=auto&amp;amp;_x_tr_tl=en&amp;amp;_x_tr_hl=de&amp;amp;_x_tr_pto=wapp&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;automatic translation&lt;/a&gt;) (1937-2006)&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip;and because one wants to be on the beach in summer in the middle of winter, I bought it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;GemäldePainting&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Signature&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kaczmarek Tadeusz was a Polish artist who worked as a painter, graphic artist and interior designer. He lived and worked mainly in the &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lower_Silesian_Voivodeship&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Lower Silesian Voivodeship&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The painting shows the beach of &lt;a href=&#34;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Boltenhagen&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Boltenhagen&lt;/a&gt;, Schleswig-Holstein on the Baltic Sea coast.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There is also a &lt;a href=&#34;https://kaczmarek-art.blogspot.com/2021/01/kaczmarek-tadeusz-1937-2006-malarstwo.html&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;blog&lt;/a&gt; with some of his works. A very similar painting is also listed there.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Translated with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.DeepL.com/Translator&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;www.DeepL.com/Translator&lt;/a&gt; (free version)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item>
